Common viva questions
1. What is a string?
A string is a sequence of characters.
2. Which function finds string length?
strlen()
3. Which function reverses a string?
strrev()
4. Which function extracts part of a string?
substr()
5. What does substr($str, 0, 5) mean?
It takes 5 characters starting from position 0.
